flowchart LR
    S1[STATE A]
    T1[GATE CHECK]
    T2[TRANSITION]
    W1[BOUND WORKFLOW]
    S2[STATE B]

    S1 ==> T1
    T1 ==> T2
    T2 ==> W1
    W1 ==> S2

    N1[conditions<br/>all / any<br/>fact checks<br/>dependency checks]
